const grammarList = ['javascript', 'python', 'typescript', 'javascriptReact', 'html', 'css', 'cpp', 'dart', 'go', 'java', 'lua', 'php', 'r', 'sql', 'json', 'jsonc', 'jsonl', 'c', 'cuda-cpp', 'xml', 'xsl']
// Import all grammar files - start
// #ifndef APP-ANDROID || APP-HARMONY
import javascriptGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/javascript.tmLanguage.json'
import pythonGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/python.tmLanguage.json'
import javascriptReactGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/javascriptReact.tmLanguage.json'
import typescriptGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/typescript.tmLanguage.json'
import htmlGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/html.tmLanguage.json'
import cssGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/css.tmLanguage.json'
import cppGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/cpp.tmLanguage.json'
import dartGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/dart.tmLanguage.json'
import goGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/go.tmLanguage.json'
import javaGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/java.tmLanguage.json'
import luaGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/lua.tmLanguage.json'
import phpGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/php.tmLanguage.json'
import rGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/r.tmLanguage.json'
import sqlGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/sql.tmLanguage.json'
import jsonGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/json.tmLanguage.json'
import jsoncGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/jsonc.tmLanguage.json'
import jsonlGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/jsonl.tmLanguage.json'
import cGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/c.tmLanguage.json'
import cudaCppGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/cuda-cpp.tmLanguage.json'
import xmlGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/xml.tmLanguage.json'
import xslGrammar from '@/chatbot/static/grammar/xsl.tmLanguage.json'
// #endif
// Import all grammar files - end
import utils from '@/chatbot/sdk/utils.uts'

import { MarkdownToken } from '@/uni_modules/uni-cmark/utssdk/interface.uts'
import { CreateHighLighter, CreateHighLighterRes, HighLighterOptions, ILineTokens } from "@/uni_modules/uni-highlight/utssdk/interface.uts"
export { MarkdownToken }
export type ParseLineCodeRes = {
	tokens: MarkdownToken[],
	language: string,
	error: string | null
}
export type ParseLineCodeCallBack = (parseLineCodeRes: ParseLineCodeRes) => void
type TmlFile = {
	scopeName : string,
	path : string
}
let uniCodeHighlighter = null as CreateHighLighterRes | null
function getTmlFile(filePaths: TmlFile[]) {
	let fileManager = uni.getFileSystemManager()
	let res = {}
	try {
		filePaths.forEach(item => {
			let content = fileManager.readFileSync(item.path, 'utf-8') as string
			res[item.scopeName] = JSON.parse(content)
		})
	} catch (err) {
		console.error('读取tml文件失败，请检查文件是否存在', err, filePaths)
		uni.showToast({
			title: '读取tml文件失败，请检查文件是否存在',
			icon: 'none'
		})
	}
	return res
}

function initUniCodeHighlighter(callBack: () => void){
	if (uniCodeHighlighter == null) {
		// #ifndef APP-ANDROID || APP-HARMONY
		// 根据 grammarList 生成tmls
		const tmls = {
			javascript: javascriptGrammar,
			python: pythonGrammar,
			typescript: typescriptGrammar,
			javascriptReact: javascriptReactGrammar,
			html: htmlGrammar,
			css: cssGrammar,
			cpp: cppGrammar,
			dart: dartGrammar,
			go: goGrammar,
			java: javaGrammar,
			lua: luaGrammar,
			php: phpGrammar,
			r: rGrammar,
			sql: sqlGrammar,
			json: jsonGrammar,
			jsonc: jsoncGrammar,
			jsonl: jsonlGrammar,
			c: cGrammar,
			"cuda-cpp": cudaCppGrammar,
			xml: xmlGrammar,
			xsl: xslGrammar
		}
		// #endif
		// #ifdef APP-ANDROID || APP-HARMONY
		const tmlsList = [] as TmlFile[]
		grammarList.forEach(item => {
			tmlsList.push({
				scopeName: item,
				path: `/chatbot/static/grammar/${item}.tmLanguage.json`
			})
		})
		// console.log('tmlsList',tmlsList)
		const tmls = getTmlFile(tmlsList)
		// #endif
		// createHighLighter({ languages: tmls } as HighLighterOptions).then((res: CreateHighLighterRes) => {
		// 	uniCodeHighlighter = res
		// 	callBack()
		// })
		uniCodeHighlighter = new CreateHighLighter({ languages: tmls } as HighLighterOptions)
		callBack()
		// console.log(tmls)
	} else {
		callBack()
	}
}

export function parseLineCode(parseLineCodeCallBack: ParseLineCodeCallBack, codeSource: string,language: string){
	if (language == 'js') language = "javascript"
	try {
		// 判断这个language是否在支持的列表中
		if (!grammarList.includes(language)) {
			// console.error('不支持解析的语言类型',language,'仅支持',grammarList.join(','))
			const res: ParseLineCodeRes = {
				tokens: [],
				language: language,
				error: '不支持解析的语言类型'
			}
			parseLineCodeCallBack(res)
			return
		}
		initUniCodeHighlighter(() => {
			// TODO: 第三个参数暂时传 0 即可，但下一个版本的 uni-highlight，需要将上一次解析返回的 state 传入 用于提升性能
			uniCodeHighlighter!.tokenizeLine(language, codeSource, 0).then((iLineToken: ILineTokens | null) => {
				utils.uniGetDispatcher("io", () => {
					// console.log('代码解析耗时 ============', Date.now() - start)
					const tokens = [] as MarkdownToken[]
					iLineToken?.tokens.forEach((tk) => {
						const token: MarkdownToken = {
							text: codeSource.substring(tk.startIndex, tk.endIndex),
							className: tk.scopes![tk.scopes!.length - 1].split(".")[0]
						}
						tokens.push(token)
					})
					// tokens.push({
					// 	text: "\n",
					// 	className: "eol"
					// });
					// console.log('tokens',tokens)
					const res: ParseLineCodeRes = {
						tokens: tokens,
						language: language,
						error: null
					}
					parseLineCodeCallBack(res)
				});
			})
		})
	} catch (error) {
		const res: ParseLineCodeRes = {
			tokens: [],
			language: language,
			// #ifdef WEB
			error: (error as any).message
			// #endif
			// #ifndef WEB
			error: error.message
			// #endif
		}
		parseLineCodeCallBack(res)
	}
}